 considered when methotrexate is used with other potentially hepatotoxic agents (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/43562/', '', 'Golimumab, Cyclosporine, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, More', 'Toremifene, Abarelix, Relugolix, Enzalutamide, Degarelix, Aminoglutethimide, Diethylstilbestrol, Histrelin, Megestrol acetate, Leuprolide, Medroxyprogesterone acetate, More', 1767369485);
